Text: thanks for your upload great group of the 80's but not for long time
Thank you! A very underrated album. One of the best. 'Specially the synth solo on "politics" and it's intro. "Praying" is great as well. Every track is awesome.

Not usually a big fan of "electronic" sound, but this album reaches me. I've always wanted to get it on CD, but man, it's like $275US on line.
  Thanks for encoding and upping.
